# Plan: Add @ai-sdk/pixelart Provider

## Context

The goal is to add a new fictional **PixelArt** AI provider to the Vercel AI SDK monorepo that supports **only image generation** (no text, no chat, no embeddings). It exposes a `createPixelArt` factory function and provider-specific image settings (size, style, pixel density). The base URL is `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1`.

The implementation follows the `@ai-sdk/luma` provider pattern exactly — the simplest image-only provider in the repo — and uses the `ImageModelV3` interface from `@ai-sdk/provider`.

---

## Reference Files

| Purpose | Path |
|---|---|
| Simplest image-only provider (template) | `packages/luma/src/luma-provider.ts` |
| Image model implementation (template) | `packages/luma/src/luma-image-model.ts` |
| Model IDs & settings types | `packages/luma/src/luma-image-settings.ts` |
| Main exports | `packages/luma/src/index.ts` |
| Version constant | `packages/luma/src/version.ts` |
| Package definition | `packages/luma/package.json` |
| Build config | `packages/luma/tsup.config.ts` |
| TS config | `packages/luma/tsconfig.json` |
| TS build config | `packages/luma/tsconfig.build.json` |
| Turbo config | `packages/luma/turbo.json` |
| Node test config | `packages/luma/vitest.node.config.js` |
| Edge test config | `packages/luma/vitest.edge.config.js` |
| ImageModelV3 interface | `packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3.ts` |
| ImageModelV3CallOptions | `packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3-call-options.ts` |
| Root TS project references | `tsconfig.json` |

---

## Implementation Steps

### Step 1 — Create `packages/pixelart/package.json`

Mirror `packages/luma/package.json`. Key differences:
- `"name": "@ai-sdk/pixelart"`
- `"version": "0.0.0"` (new package; changeset will manage version)
- Remove `prepack`/`postpack` scripts (no docs to copy yet; no MDX file)
- Keep all other fields identical (license, scripts, exports, deps, engines, publishConfig, etc.)

```json
{
  "name": "@ai-sdk/pixelart",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "sideEffects": false,
  "main": "./dist/index.js",
  "module": "./dist/index.mjs",
  "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
  "files": ["dist/**/*", "src", "!src/**/*.test.ts", "!src/**/*.test-d.ts", "!src/**/__snapshots__", "!src/**/__fixtures__", "CHANGELOG.md", "README.md"],
  "scripts": {
    "build": "pnpm clean && tsup --tsconfig tsconfig.build.json",
    "build:watch": "pnpm clean && tsup --watch",
    "clean": "del-cli dist docs *.tsbuildinfo",
    "type-check": "tsc --build",
    "test": "pnpm test:node && pnpm test:edge",
    "test:update": "pnpm test:node -u",
    "test:watch": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js",
    "test:edge": "vitest --config vitest.edge.config.js --run",
    "test:node": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js --run"
  },
  "exports": {
    "./package.json": "./package.json",
    ".": {
      "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
      "import": "./dist/index.mjs",
      "require": "./dist/index.js"
    }
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@ai-sdk/provider": "workspace:*",
    "@ai-sdk/provider-utils": "workspace:*"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@ai-sdk/test-server": "workspace:*",
    "@types/node": "20.17.24",
    "@vercel/ai-tsconfig": "workspace:*",
    "tsup": "^8",
    "typescript": "5.8.3",
    "zod": "3.25.76"
  },
  "peerDependencies": { "zod": "^3.25.76 || ^4.1.8" },
  "engines": { "node": ">=18" },
  "publishConfig": { "access": "public" },
  "homepage": "https://ai-sdk.dev/docs",
  "repository": { "type": "git", "url": "git+https://github.com/vercel/ai.git" },
  "bugs": { "url": "https://github.com/vercel/ai/issues" },
  "keywords": ["ai"]
